<HEADLINE>
<P>
GUNS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We cannot stop the flow of drugs into this country, so by what marvelous, 
wonderful miracle are we going to stop the flow of restricted weapons? The 
criminal will always be well armed; only the private citizen will be denied 
access to the marketplace. 
</P>
<P>
LORI GRAHAM, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
